title: Quarto Demo
text:
Chart
Figure 1 shows a relationship between wt and mpg features in the MTCars dataset.

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(mtcars, aes(x = wt, y = mpg)) +
    geom_point(color = "#0099f9", size = 5)




Figure 1: Weight of vehicle per 1000lbs (wt) vs. Miles/Gallon (mpg)
